# MAISON AMIIR

> MAISON AMIIR is a Paris-inspired luxury perfume house with its Creative Studio in India. We blend French artistry,
> French sophistication, and Indian heritage into small-batch signature fragrances
> We do not create perfumes. We create signatures.
> Shop at https://maisonamiir.com

## About
- Founded to restore perfumery to its true essence
- Small-batch blends using premium-grade oils
- Long-lasting performance with soft, refined presence
- Philosophy: Quiet luxury — subtle, elegant, deeply personal
- Independent fragrance house — not affiliated with any designer brand

